sql:
SELECT value, description
FROM config_values
WHERE config_id = 0;

SELECT layout_algorithm_name 
FROM layout_algorithms 
WHERE created_by = 2;

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM graph_edges
WHERE is_public = 'true';

SELECT graph_type_name
FROM graph_types
WHERE is_directed = 0;

SELECT theme_name, COUNT(*) AS theme_count
FROM graph_themes
GROUP BY theme_name;

SELECT COUNT(graph_id) AS total_modified_graphs
FROM graphs
WHERE last_modified_date BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-05-31';

SELECT label_type, COUNT(*) AS label_count
FROM graph_labels
GROUP BY label_type;

external_knowledge:
'birth of all graph themes' refers to the creation date of each graph theme, which is stored in the 'created_date' column; 
'now' refers to the current date; 
Julian days are a continuous count of days since January 1, 4713 BCE (in the Julian period).

